and post the resulting story on Slashdot." Read below for the story of
how Mr. Laine's [2]detailed reply and rebuttal to that Slashdot
discussion came about. TropicalCoder asks, "After reading LiftPort's
rebuttal to Slashdot critics, do any of you now feel your pessimism
somewhat dispelled?"

